 65+  8712              ; CRtoATTR - Converts a screen char coord  into a ATTR Address  b,c = y,x positions
 66+  8712              ;	IN  - B=Row, C=Column
 67+  8712              ;	OUT - HL=Address in screen also stored in (SCR_ATTR_PTR)
 68+  8712              ;	Conversion:
 69+  8712              ;			Row FFfff   Column CCCCC
